description: aUSDC represents USDC supplied to the AAVE protocol. By depositing aUSDC into Pendle, users can earn a fixed APY on their aUSDC. The yield is generated by forfeiting the right to claim aUSDC's variable APY in the AAVE protocol. Withdrawing will become available after the maturity date. If you want to withdraw before the maturity date you can do so in Pendle's web app
